column5: SAN FRANCISCO  April 10 For the first time in the era of the modern automobile  the most valuable U.S. car maker is not based in Detroit.

column4: Qualcomm hits back at Apple's lawsuit  accuses iPhone maker of false statements
column5: Qualcomm Inc hit back at Apple Inc's charges that were made in a U.S. lawsuit in January  saying the iPhone maker breached agreements with the firm and encouraged regulatory attacks on its business in various jurisdictions around the world by making false statements.
